Amazing environment, service and food quality.
Toanle offered super great service and advice for our lunch meal and cocktails at Citron restaurant, intercontinental resort Da Nang. His cocktail, Monkey Tail is a bit strong with special favor made from Vietnamese rum. The restaurant environment is amazing and we enjoyed our first day lunch here. Great !!!
