HoChin L wrote a review Feb 2024
Barcelona, Spain158 contributions48 helpful votes
+1
Matchless wonderful hotel with top service quality and architecture.
An eye-opening magical hotel where one meets the top quality hotel/room design. From Heaven level to Sky, Earth, and Sea; although expensive, the quality one experiences here worth the money spent. Every staff is kind and professional in offering their services and care. Love their L_O_N_G Bar where I can actually be relaxed and space-out, it's a must-visit! Need to mention their top-class kids club as well, my son loooooves staying there. Afternoon tea at Citron is abundant and tasty, love the scones and side mascarpone and jams! Definitely a place where I'd love to re-visit.
