Exceptionally kind assistance in emergency
We stayed there for New Year holidays and were deeply touched by kindness from the hotel at our unexpected change in schedule. Our plan was to indulge in this special resort for a couple of days, but we found out that we would need to check out the next day due to an emergency at home soon after we had checked in. Ms. Hong Le, who assisted us during check-in and consequently early check-out, showed us extraordinary compassion about us by offering that the hotel would cover incidental charges such as restaurants meals since the accommodation would be nonrefundable. Because her generous offer sounded beyond our imagination, we first thought we mistook her since English is not our mother tongue. Ms. Le, then brought a Japanese speaking staff, Ms. Ngan to explain and help ensure…
